11774, "(fr)Bei, there are Vishnans shrieking in the back of my brain. You might want to ask yourself why they don't let you see them."

11775, "(fr)Please, Sublieutenant, I don't know what you're seeing, but let me help you."

11776, "(fr)Don't you understand? The Vishnans stand for what's good in this universe! If we revert to savagery, if we fail to end this war, they'll abandon us to the Shivans!"

11777, "(fr)Maybe if they were so absolutely good they wouldn't do things like that!"

11778, "(fr)If you're not part of their design, Laporte, then who's speaking to you? They shaped my entire life! Who's been playing with yours? There's only one other option!"

11779, "(fr)Then they're the only option humanity has left!"

11780, "(fr)They are coming. I will hide you from their sight as they hunt for you. Find the way out before they drive you mad."

11781, "(fr)Their Keeper aspects are assaulting you! Evade now!"

11782, "(fr)They must not follow you. They must never know who and what you are. If they learn, we will both die. So hurry, Miss Laporte, hurry onwards."

11783, "(fr)They're coming up out of Bei's memories. The ships, Laporte, beware the ships."

