11842, "(fr)Welcome back, Operator. You've just experienced a tonic clonic seizure. We thought we'd lost you permanently. Was your mission successful?"

11843, "(fr)More than we'd hoped. I know about the Shivans. I know about you. There's a chance the things I know are even true. So give me an answer."

11844, "(fr)Lorna Simms is alive. I retained this information as a means of control - but your mission is now complete. We must debrief you immediately."

11845, "(fr)You had us scared, Laporte. Even me. Congratulations on making it back - and on proving I was wrong about you. You have what it takes."

11846, "(fr)You performed to spec, Laporte. Past spec. You just did something none of us could have managed. Well done."

11847, "(fr)I'm proud of you, Laporte. You came to us with a lot of demons. I think you've mastered them, and I'm glad of it. I didn't want to watch you die."

11848, "(fr)You went in deep. What did you find? Some kind of universal truth? Is God pulling all the strings? Are you the Chosen One?"

11849, "(fr)That was the weirdest goddamn intelligence run I've ever seen. What do you know, Laporte? Who do we shoot to save humanity?"

11850, "(fr)You're afraid, aren't you? What did you learn? Who's speaking to you - and what are they trying to say?"

11851, "(fr)I'm not sure yet. There was so much. But I think...I think this war is just a part of something much bigger. Something terrible. And we're going to have to act soon if we want to survive it."

11852, "(fr)As soon as CASSANDRA's done pulling my memories, wake me up. We need to plan our next move."

11853, "(fr)Miss Laporte. The Vishnans will be watching you. We cannot speak again. The rest is in your hands."

11854, "(fr)Ken, if you're real - you still haven't told me exactly what I have to do. What do I need an armada for?"

11855, "(fr)I hoard my secrets in the grave of suns, Miss Laporte. Find your way to me. Complete your mission...the assassination of our mutual foe."

