13162, "(fr)Negative, Katana. I cannot obey that order until every man, woman and child has been evacuated."

13163, "(fr)God DAMN it. That glorious, stubborn, short-sighted jackass. He won't do it."

13164, "(fr)We have another way. We can force the Tevs to detonate the bomb if we disrupt their boarding operation. Then we jump clear."

13165, "(fr)Federation warship, you are endangering the lives of tens of thousands of your own citizens. Stand down, or be destroyed."

13166, "(fr)Then we have to. Either we destroy the station with our guns - a long shot at best - or we find another way to deny it to the Tevs."

13167, "(fr)This is Simak Station. We have been boarded by GTVA marines. On the condition that my charges remain unharmed, I surrender this station and the personnel aboard."

13168, "(fr)I've designated Simak Station as a hostile target. One way or another, we have to destroy it. God help us all."

13169, "(fr)I need three minutes to get the gate ready. If you can keep the Tevs from triggering for two minutes, I can get my ship clear. If not, so be it."

13170, "(fr)Sir, GTVA forces are withdrawing! Detecting a pulse transmission to the warhead! It's going hot!"

13171, "(fr)The firing sequence is underway. Sensors give us fifty seconds. We're scrambling to open the gate, stand by..."

13172, "(fr)God damn you all to hell. I hope you can live with what you did today, Captain Genady, because twenty thousand people won't. Simak Station, signing off. "

13173, "(fr)The gate is live! Altan Orde, jumping clear! I'll see you at the rendezvous, Ivan. Stay safe."

13174, "(fr)Ivan, we're not going to make it. It's been an honor and a privilege. Take a few down for us."

13175, "(fr)Thirty seconds to detonation! Stand by to jump!"

13176, "(fr)Detonation underway! Brace, brace, brace!"

13177, "(fr)Point defense units report succcessful engagement on all Borealis and Cancer wing bombers."

13178, "(fr)Attention all Third Fleet Units. This is Admiral Calder. A massive GTVA attack is underway across Jovian space. I am declaring Case Kodiak. Enact scorched earth protocols."

13179, "(fr)Sir, I estimate the Tevs will withdraw and detonate the bomb if we destroy a few of the transports or badly damage the corvette."

13180, "(fr)Two minutes to gate readiness. Keep them from triggering a little longer if you can."

13181, "(fr)One minute to departure! You can probably risk disrupting their attack further, Katana. We're in the clear."

13182, "(fr)Ivan, we're - *static*"

13183, "(fr)The Altan Orde is gone, sir. No pods."

13184, "(fr)Boanerges bombers moving in on us. Flight, can you recall our Gamma wing from the Io flux station?"

13185, "(fr)Gamma wing is on station. Ready for orders."

13186, "(fr)We need to destroy Simak Station, sir. We can't leave it in GTVA hands. Destroying it could buy us months, maybe years."

13187, "(fr)God damn you to hell. I hope you can live with what you're about to do, Captain Genady, because twenty thousand people won't. This is a betrayal of everything the Federation stands for."

13188, "(fr)It's done. Simak Station has been nullified as a potential GTVA asset. We need to get to a rally point, sir."

13189, "(fr)We need to withdraw to a rally point, sir. We can't hold this position. Jump drive ready."

13190, "(fr)Getting some armor spall off the Triteia. Attempting to exploit openings."

13191, "(fr)That's a hit, that's a palpable hit. I think we took out a big structural member."

13192, "(fr)Boom. Scratch one Diomedes. Beautiful kill, sir."

13193, "(fr)I've lost telemetry from all Gamma fighters."

13194, "(fr)If we destroy the transports, we can end the boarding now. But if you want to give the Altan Orde time, we need to duel the Triteia - and make sure we don't drive her off too quickly."

